data.description: Charming 3/2 only 1 mile from the Augusta National! Open concept split floor plan is perfect for everyday living. Owner suite features a glass walk in shower! Enjoy time with your favorite people in the large living room with wood burning fireplace and built in bookshelves. The huge backyard was built for entertaining with the extra large patio area. Long driveway and side entry garage leave lots of room for company! Walking distance to the course makes this an ideal tournament rental opportunity!
